modules.description: This module implements a buffer pooling mechanism that reuses or creates buffers of a specified size on demand. It works with a custom buffer type provided by the parameter module `B`, allowing efficient allocation and release of buffers for handling data chunks. Concrete use cases include optimizing memory usage in networking applications or streaming data processing where frequent buffer allocations and deallocations occur.
